org.gvsig.chart

Interface ChartManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Manager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultChartManager

    public interface ChartManager
extends Manager
    This class is responsible of the management of the ChartServices library. It is the library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage ChartServices.
    See Also:
    ChartService, GroupedCharts, ChartProperties, ChartServiceManager
